{"tid":1356404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母！義士唔係condom呀！！成個熱門都係何妖老母個墳同埋啲垃圾流言","createTime":"2019-07-23T13:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T15:16:03.000Z","uid":4705,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"526c8bb8cbf1b9f9dd2cbb0930c95b0c15cad0b0","tid":1356404,"uid":4705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:22:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>連垃圾韓團站姐都上到熱門<br />\n冇人記得721有義士比人爆頭？<br />\n屌你老味係咪冇人記得前線義士呀！！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7.21 上環清場兩日後　警至今未交代發射彈藥種類數量、受傷人數<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355354\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355354</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n咁大穫無人講? ７２１上環最恐怖１分鐘半片段流出 !!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351301\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351301</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[整合] 7.21上環開槍清場 有片有圖！ - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348209\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348209</a><br />\n<br />\n黑警上環開左36槍 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1345680\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1345680</a><br />\n<br />\n721 上環開槍整合 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348232\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348232</a>[/size=2][/b]"},{"pid":"51a0622c968c78e5abad2ee1a6370c25d0fed1a8","tid":1356404,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:24:02.000Z","msg":"異士同你講佢地需要光環嗎？"},{"pid":"76cc52a7d4e040cd465bb165056e16d9b7a52b85","tid":1356404,"uid":4705,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51a0622c968c78e5abad2ee1a6370c25d0fed1a8","tid":1356404,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:24:02.000Z","msg":"異士同你講佢地需要光環嗎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:25:07.000Z","msg":"收聲啦IVE仔"},{"pid":"c34ae6ee61c4e63f884029f5653e5b528113fe9a","tid":1356404,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76cc52a7d4e040cd465bb165056e16d9b7a52b85","tid":1356404,"uid":4705,"like